  "title": "A spinning star-like UFO sighted near Curitiba [2001]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/12/1366/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-m2",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>APRIL 28th, 2001</strong>. Time: 10:00 pm. Duration: 15 minutes. In the Cabral district, city of Curitiba, State of Paraná, two witnesses spotted with the naked eye and also with the use of binoculars a yellow and red star-like UFO, in a rotating movement. The UFO was flying straight towards the Northeast. In the observations of the COMDABRA [Brazilian Aerospace Defense Command] the witness &#8220;reported that the observed object revolved around its own axis and was also observed by his wife.&#8221;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.608. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni no bairro Cabral, Curitiba, Paraná&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n",
